################
# In the form of <type>: <subject>
# The title should be less than 50 characters / Clearly state what the changes are / No period at the end
# Ex) feat: add login function
#
# Make sure to leave a blank line after the title
#
################
# Describe the changes in detail, preferably within 72 characters.
# Make sure to prefix list items with a dash (-)
#
################
# Optionally, you can add a footer to reference issues
# Ex) Close #1
#
################
# Types
#
# Feat : New feature
# Fix : Bug fix
# Docs : Documentation
# Style : Code formatting, semicolon missing, no code changes
# Refactor : Code refactoring
# Test : Test code, refactoring test code added
# Chore : Package manager modification, etc., other modifications ex) .gitignore
# Comment : Add or change comments in the code
# Rename : File or folder name changes
# Remove : File deletion
# !BREAKING CHANGE : Major changes that require attention
# !HOTFIX : Urgent corrections
#
################
# Example
# Feat : add login function
#
# - Login API added
# - JWT token issue function added
#
# Close #1
################